  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个TLS 1.3握手的状态图，从初始状态开始，经过Start，然后进入SendClientHello发送客户端问候，接着等待服务器响应。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Start",
        "SendClientHello",
        "WaitServerHello"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那从WaitServerHello之后呢？如果收到有效的ServerHello，应该进入什么状态？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitServerHello",
        "DeriveHPKE"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "收到有效ServerHello后进入DeriveHPKE状态，完成密钥派生，然后进入SendAuth发送认证信息，再到WaitAuth等待认证结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "DeriveHPKE",
        "SendAuth",
        "WaitAuth"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我已经把DeriveHPKE到SendAuth再到WaitAuth的流转加上了。WaitAuth这里需要分支吗？比如认证成功和失败的情况？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitAuth",
        "Established",
        "Error"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，WaitAuth要分出两条路径：认证成功进入Established状态，认证失败进入Error终止。另外Established之后还需要支持会话密钥更新。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WaitAuth",
        "Established",
        "Error",
        "Rekey"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下，SessionKeyUpdate触发从Established到Rekey的转换，然后Rekey完成后回到Established，形成循环，对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Established",
        "Rekey",
        "SessionKeyUpdate"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "没错，Rekey完成后回到Established，这样密钥更新可以多次进行。还有，初始状态我用[*]表示，指向Start。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "[*]",
        "Start"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "完成了，整个状态流转都画好了：从初始状态到Start，经过握手各阶段，认证分支处理，以及Established后的密钥更新循环。",
